<code><span class=3D"inline-comment-marker" data-ref=3D"a0ba8702-dfd1-487d-=
906d-1f1bf6601510">Generated and filled by Mesh library</span></code></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
in the x-AddnAuthorisation Header call from Channels to PingAuth</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Base64-encoded JSON structure containing a mobile device's fingerprint or R=
SA JavaScript value.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<code>string</code></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
No</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
None</td>
