rong>, 150.172.238.178, 10.0.0.1</span></p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
&nbsp;Pick up the first value from this header value.<span>&nbsp;</span><sp=
an style=3D"color: rgb(17,17,17);">X-Forwarded-For</span></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Source IP address of the device that generated the HTTP request.</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<code>string</code></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Yes</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
