<br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<br></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<p><span>name of the key, which includes:</span></p>
<ol>
<li><span>PAYEEPAYIDTYPE</span></li>
<li><span>PAYEEPAYIDVALUE</span></li>
<li><span>SOURCE</span></li>
<li><span>COUNTER</span></li>
<li><span>COUNTER_24HOUR</span></li>
</ol><p><br></p><p><span>Below is a summary of the fields:</span></p><p><sp=
an>PAYEEPAYIDTYPE</span></p><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span><em>'MO=
BILE', 'EMAIL, 'LANDLINE', 'ABN', 'FREEFORM'</em></span></p><p><span>PAYEEP=
AYIDVALUE</span></p><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span><em>Actual mobi=
le number, actual email address etc</em></span></p><p><span>SOURCE</span></=
p><p style=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span><em>Page where the resolution was=
 made (e.g. Add Beneficiary)</em></span></p><p><span>COUNTER</span></p><p s=
tyle=3D"margin-left: 40.0px;"><span><em>Integer - number of times resolutio=
n was attempted since the PayID was actually consumed (tracked at session l=
evel)</em></span></p><p><span>COUNTER_24HOUR</span></p><p style=3D"margin-l=
eft: 40.0px;"><span>Integer =E2=80=93 total number of times resolution was =
attempted in calendar day (midnight to midnight - AEST). Hard daily limit (=
regardless of successful resolution or not).&nbsp; Does not reset.</span></=
p></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
<code>string</code></td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Yes</td>
<td style=3D"text-align: left;vertical-align: top;" class=3D"confluenceTd">=
Example:<span>&nbsp;</span><code>TRANSACTIONTYPE</code></td>
</tr>
<tr class=3D"">
